    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hindu semi-divine beings that are half human and half serpentine. They are often associated with waters, such as rivers, lakes, rain, and seas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
